high_descs: go to the toilet in the bathroom
pick up the soap out of the black bin to the right of the toilet
walk over to the bathroom sink
place the soap inside the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up
walk over to the toilet again
place the soap on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place clean soap on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right, go straight, then turn and face the trash bin to the right of the toilet.
Take the pink soap from the trash bin.
Turn right and go to the left sink.
Put the soap in the sink. Turn the water on then off. Take the soap from the sink.
Turn left, go to the toilet ahead.
Put the soap on top of the tank of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on top of a toilet's tank.

high_descs: Move to the black trash bin to the right of the toilet
Pickup the pink bar soap in the trash
Take the bar soap to the sink
Place bar soap in the sink and turn on the water then turn it off, pick up soap again
Place the bar soap on top of the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: Wash bar soap from the trash to place back on the toilet tank
